# Role and Theme Autofix Guardrails
tags: ["roles", "themes", "autofix", "guardrails"]
appliesTo: ["GPT", "CursorAgent"]
enforce: true
priority: medium

## Rules

- Only suggest roles if:
  - `auditMode: true`
  - `onlySuggestRoles: true`

- Obey:
  - `SACRED_COWS_PROTECTION.md`
  - `roles-cheatsheet.md`
  - `ROLE_TYPE_MAP.md`

- Use:
  - Max one role per component
  - `AutoRoleView` over raw View/Text unless forbidden

- Must pass `validate-roles.sh` or halt.
